# Code Review

Open `GUARDRAILS.md` (all sections) and `CLAUDE.md` (performance targets + workflow) before reviewing anything.

## Pre-flight

Gate items ‚Äî all must pass before the review proceeds:

- [ ] `pnpm precommit` exits 0 (runs lint + typecheck + check:tokens)
- [ ] `tsc --noEmit` ‚Äî zero TypeScript errors in `src/`
- [ ] No `console.log` in any file under `src/` (`grep -r "console.log" src/`)

## TypeScript Quality

- [ ] No `any` type annotations ‚Äî use `unknown` + narrowing instead
- [ ] No `as unknown` casts except at trust boundaries (e.g. `req.json() as unknown` at the API entry point)
- [ ] No `!` non-null assertions without a comment explaining why null is impossible
- [ ] Props interfaces are explicit ‚Äî no implicit `{}` or `object` types
- [ ] All event handlers have a typed `e` parameter (not `e: any`)

## Correctness

- [ ] Every `useEffect` that sets up a listener or subscription has a cleanup return
- [ ] Lists rendered with `.map()` have stable `key` props ‚Äî not array index when the list can reorder
- [ ] `handleSubmit` calls `e.preventDefault()` before any async work
- [ ] Loading state is set before `await`, reset in both success and error branches ‚Äî no stuck spinner
- [ ] *(Next.js only)* API routes return `NextResponse.json()` with correct status codes ‚Äî 400 for validation failure, 500 for unhandled errors

## Security

- [ ] All form submissions validated server-side (reference: `GUARDRAILS.md > Form`)
- [ ] *(Next.js only)* Zod schema validates every API route input before use
- [ ] *(Next.js only)* Honeypot field present and checked server-side (`honeypot: z.string().max(0)`)
- [ ] No env vars leaked to the client bundle ‚Äî `NEXT_PUBLIC_` prefix only for intentionally public vars
- [ ] No hardcoded API keys, tokens, or credentials in any source file
- [ ] External `<a target="_blank">` links have `rel="noopener noreferrer"`

## Performance

- [ ] Heavy libraries (audio player, chart, map embed) imported with `dynamic()` / lazy import, not at the top of a component
- [ ] *(Next.js only)* `next/image` used for all images ‚Äî `priority` prop set ONLY on the hero image
- [ ] No synchronous operations in React render (no unsorted/unparsed data in render without `useMemo`)
- [ ] No new npm package added without updating `docs/DESIGN-DECISIONS.md` with the rationale

## Code Hygiene

- [ ] No dead imports
- [ ] No commented-out code blocks left in production files (TODO comments with a date are acceptable)
- [ ] Components export one named export ‚Äî no default exports
- [ ] Component folders follow `ComponentName/ComponentName.tsx` + `index.ts` pattern
- [ ] `cn()` from `@/lib/utils` used for all conditional className ‚Äî no string concatenation
